  "base_path": "/carers-allowance-report-change",
  "content_id": "ccada790-545a-4f23-b931-e5bb84464c50",
  "description": "Report changes in circumstances if you're claiming or have applied for Carer's Allowance - if you get a job, take a break from caring for someone, stop being a carer",
  "details": {
    "department_analytics_profile": "",
    "external_related_links": [

    ],
    "introductory_paragraph": "<p>You must report changes in circumstances if you’re claiming or have applied for Carer’s Allowance, for example if:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>you change, start or leave your job</li>\n  <li>you start earning more than £139 a week</li>\n  <li>you stop being a carer</li>\n  <li>you stop providing at least 35 hours of care a week</li>\n  <li>you take a holiday or go into hospital - even if you arrange care while you’re away</li>\n  <li>the person you care for goes into hospital, into a care home or takes a holiday</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>You cannot use this service to report the death of someone you’re caring for. You should use the <a href=\"/after-a-death/organisations-you-need-to-contact-and-tell-us-once\">Tell Us Once</a> service instead.</p>\n\n<div role=\"note\" aria-label=\"Information\" class=\"application-notice info-notice\">\n<p>This guide is also available <a href=\"/lwfans-gofalwr-hysbysu-newidiadau\">in Welsh (Cymraeg)</a>.</p>\n</div>\n\n<h2 id=\"report-changes-online\">Report changes online</h2>\n\n<p>Make sure you have:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>your National Insurance number</li>\n  <li>details of the person you’re caring for</li>\n  <li>details of your changes</li>\n</ul>\n",
    "more_information": "<p>This will take around 10 minutes.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"other-ways-to-apply\">Other ways to apply</h2>\n<p>You can also report a change of circumstances to the <a href=\"/carers-allowance-unit\">Carer’s Allowance Unit</a> by phone or by post.</p>\n\n<div role=\"note\" aria-label=\"Information\" class=\"application-notice info-notice\">\n<p>Because of coronavirus (COVID-19) it’s quicker to report changes of circumstances online.</p>\n</div>\n",
    "start_button_text": "Start now",
    "transaction_start_link": "https://www.carersallowance.service.gov.uk/ui-citizen-cofc/change-selection",
    "variants": [

    ],
    "will_continue_on": "the Carer's Allowance service"
  },
